        \"Source inspection: `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/domain/model/MenuItem.kt` contains only scalar menu fields and no permission or protected API calls.\",\n+          \"Target inspection: `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/domain/discovery_models.cj::MenuItemData` and `::DetailMenuItemData` keep menu-item data pure while `detail_store.cj` and `cart_store.cj` consume it without permission logic.\",\n+          \"Focused test evidence: `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_repository_contract_test.cj` and `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase05_detail_cart_state_mutations_test.cj` both exercise translated menu-item data flows, confirming the phase-05 target uses these models without any permission-gated behavior.\"\n+        ],\n+        \"parityLevel\": \"not-applicable\",\n+        \"targetEndpoints\": [\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/domain/discovery_models.cj::MenuItemData\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/domain/discovery_models.cj::DetailMenuItemData\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/cart/cart_store.cj::buildState\"\n+        ],\n+        \"tests\": [\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_repository_contract_test.cj\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase05_detail_cart_state_mutations_test.cj\"\n+        ],\n+        \"notes\": \"Source override: static analysis attached a runtime-permission feature to a model file that only carries menu metadata. No permission behavior exists in either source or target model surfaces.\",\n+        \"coverageFacts\": {\n+          \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n+          \"closureKind\": \"not-applicable\",\n+          \"parityKind\": \"not-applicable\",\n+          \"sourceBehaviorMapped\": true,\n+          \"targetBehaviorImplemented\": false,\n+          \"activeSimplification\": {\n+            \"used\": false,\n+            \"reason\": \"\",\n+            \"preservedBehaviors\": [],\n+            \"omittedBe